== 發行 ==
本片原定2015年7月31日上映<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/john-greens-paper-towns-film-722906 |title=John Green's 'Paper Towns' Film Adaptation Gets Release Date |last=Kilday |first=Gregg |date=2014-08-01 |website= |publisher=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |accessdate=2014-08-02 |archive-date=2015-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150627074550/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/john-greens-paper-towns-film-722906 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，後來改至6月19日<ref name=citizen-times>{{cite web|url=http://www.citizen-times.com/story/carol-motsinger/2014/10/27/paper-towns-charlotte-filming/18011609/|title='Paper Towns' will begin filming in Charlotte next week|publisher=citizen-times.com|author=Carol Motsinger|date=2014-10-27|accessdate=2014-11-14|archive-date=2019-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913055908/https://www.citizen-times.com/story/carol-motsinger/2014/10/27/paper-towns-charlotte-filming/18011609/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後又改至同年6月5日<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/books/2014/12/23/john-green-the-fault-in-our-stars-author-of-the-year/20775795/ | title=Author of the Year: John Green | work=USA Today | date=2014-12-23 | accessdate=2014-12-23 | author=McClurg, Jocelyn | archive-date=2015-11-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151110102253/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/books/2014/12/23/john-green-the-fault-in-our-stars-author-of-the-year/20775795/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年3月，最後選定於2015年7月24日推出，這原為《[[鬼哭神嚎：惡靈15|鬼哭神嚎：惡靈15]]》的發行日<ref>{{cite news|last1=Lesnick|first1=Silas|title=20th Century Fox Shifts Dates for Spy, Poltergeist and Paper Towns|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/416235-20th-century-fox-swaps-shifts-dates-for-spy-poltergeist-and-paper-towns|accessdate=2015-03-09|publisher=comingsoon.net|date=2015-03-04|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612181724/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/416235-20th-century-fox-swaps-shifts-dates-for-spy-poltergeist-and-paper-towns|dead-url=no}}</ref>。台灣原定2015年8月28日上映，但由於[[驚奇四超人|驚奇四超人]]的票房慘賠，於上映三個禮拜前取消，改為發行DVD。

=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]專業新鮮度55%<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/paper_towns/ |title=Paper Towns |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2015-07-27 |archive-date=2019-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190916125627/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/paper_towns |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分57<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/paper-towns | title=Paper Towns | work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] | accessdate=2015-07-06 | archive-date=2018-06-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180629064258/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/paper-towns | dead-url=no }}</ref>，整體評價普通，影評人主要認為電影深度不足，但仍獲得一般青少年男女的青睞。

=== 票房 ===
